<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu'n A kiu, A hun sam,
 Chaute'n ei hun zuon un ti'n;
 Ama'n A hun hukdam thei,

[V2]
 Aw kawt hawng lien un!
 Aw kawt hawng lien un,
 Aw kawt hawng lien un;
 Ama'n A hun hukdam thei,
 Aw kawt hawng lien un.

[V3]
 2. A kiu, hukdam di'n A hung,
 Nang di'n A hinna A piei;
 Than chungah A guolzo tai,
 Aw kawt hawng lien un!

[V4]
 3. Isu chun, A kiu zing hi,
 Na utna cheng Amah pie'n;
 Na lung sukipak ina,
 Aw kawt hawng lien un!

[V5]
 4. Isun A kiu hun bei zel,
 Hukdamna a naih lai hin
 Hukdampa'n A hun pelh ma'n,
 Aw kawt hawng lien un.</lyrics>
<title>OPEN WIDE THE DOOR</title>
<hymn_number>239</hymn_number>
</song>